Sentencas: A low temperature (<= 650 degrees C) process for fabricating nano-structured (La, Sr) (Ga, Mg, Co)O(3-delta) (LSGMC) electrolyte/(La, Sr) (Co, Fe)O(3-delta)-(Gd, Ce)O(2-delta) (LSCF-GDC) cathode films, similar to 7 and similar to 25 mu m in thickness, respectively, was developed using an aerosol deposition (AD) process for use in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: NiO-GDC was used as an anode substrate in anode-supported type cells.
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: The deposited LSGMC electrolyte and LSCF-GDC composite cathode film maintained good adhesion with the NiO-GDC anode, even though the coating processes were completed at the room temperature.
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: The LSGMC electrolyte was composed of nano-sized grains smaller than 30 nm.
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the LSGMC electrolyte fabricated at room-temperature was similar to 30 mS/cm at 650 degrees
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: C. The LSCF-GDC composite cathode showed >= 20% porosity with a grain size <= 100 nm.
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition

Sentencas: The peak power density of the LSGMC electrolyte-based, anode-supported-type cell with the nano-structured LSCF-GDC cathode produced at room-temperature by AD was 0.39 W/cm(2) at 650 degrees C. (C) 2011
Titulo: Low temperature preparation and characterization of LSGMC based IT-SOFC cell by aerosol deposition
